Question: An image includes an anemone with white tendrils and a thick red stalk surrounded by something purplish.

Reference Answer: True

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Does the image include an anemone?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Does the image include an anemone?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Are the tendrils white?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Are the tendrils white?')
ANSWER4=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the stalk thick and red?')
ANSWER5=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the stalk thick and red?')
ANSWER6=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the anemone surrounded by something purplish?')
ANSWER7=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the anemone surrounded by something purplish?')
ANSWER8=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER2} and {ANSWER4} and {ANSWER6}')
ANSWER9=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} and {ANSWER3} and {ANSWER5} and {ANSWER7}')
ANSWER10=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER8} xor {ANSWER9}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER10)
```
